-- Power Producer CEZ to Spin Off Renewable Resources, Lidove Noviny Says
-- B y   L a d k a   B a u e r o v a
-- 2012-01-06T08:17:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-06/power-producer-cez-to-spin-off-renewable-resources-lidove-noviny-says.html
CEZ AS (CEZ) , the largest Czech power
producer, plans to regroup its renewable resources in a separate
unit and sell part of it to pre-selected “qualified”
investors, Lidove Noviny reported, citing spokesman Martin
Schreier.  Another possibility is to sell the unit on the stock
exchange, the newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ladka Bauerova at 
 lbauerova@bloomberg.net  